metadata.name: BEEPLE x 10KTF Physical Hoodie
metadata.description: This NFT represents a physical one of one 10KTF x 0N1 Force Hoodie that BEEPLE drew his own unique art onto, thus creating the first BEEPLE x 10KTF physical hoodie. The NFT showcases not only a rotating 3D representation of the hoodie, but also shows footage of BEEPLE drawing on the hoodie and creating the piece live at the event. You can see him laughing as he draws all over the fabric and the crowd watches in awe. The total amount of time spent on the piece was a little over thirty five minutes. Once he was finished I gave him a hug and asked for a picture with him and the hoodie, to which he agreed. The owner of this NFT will inherit the ownership of the one of one 10KTF x BEEPLE physical hoodie.
